{"type": "article", "id": 2725, "title": "Nike Flyknit Roshe Run 新系列", "description": "", "date": "2014-10-09T07:45:40Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [], "category": 25, "column": 28, "author": 1329, "comment_count": 0, "praise_count": 7, "image": "img/article/article_show/20160605232452q3jZBnFlw9yIrv4c.jpeg", "contents": "\n\n<p>\r\n\tFlyknit 为 Nike 研发出来的一种以轻薄透气为主要特性的编织鞋面。日前，Nike 为其 Roshe Run 系列加入Flyknit 编织鞋面，推出全新配色款式，延续了 Roshe Run 简单的鞋形轮廓，鞋面采用拼接的形式，将紫色、粉色、橘色搭配，显出活泼热情的感觉，同时，鞋带与内衬选择了黑色，鞋底与 logo 选用白色，使得整个鞋子更加耐看。这一系列已于 10 月 4 日上线 Nike 官方网上商店，定价 125 美元，<a href=\"http://www.nike.com/us/en_us/c/launch/2014-10/nike-roshe-flyknit\" target=\"_blank\">点击这里尝试购买</a>。\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160605232451zwfrWoANTU8mtDIv.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.0\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/201606052324514HijelLR08sdoYXQ.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.0\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/20160605232451jgh5u09GdcwUmaoO.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.0\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n\t<br>\r\n</p>\r\n<div>\r\n\t<br>\r\n</div>\n\n\n"}